                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rvt-section rvt-theme-light " data-sb-section="card-teaser">
            <div class="rvt-container">
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    <div class="rvt-section-intro rvt-section-intro--center ">
            <div class="rvt-section-intro__eyebrow">Academics</div>
        <h2 class="rvt-section-intro__title">Learn without limits. Lead with purpose.</h2>
            <div class="rvt-section-intro__teaser">
            <p data-end="464" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="" data-start="62">From the nation&#8217;s number one public affairs school to top-ranked business and arts programs, IU leads. Across disciplines, world-renowned faculty and students work together to tackle complex, real-world challenges&#8212;thinking critically and applying knowledge in ways that shape industries, communities, and the future.</p>
        </div>
                                <div class="rvt-section-intro__actions">
            <a class="rvt-button rvt-button--cta" href="/academics/degrees-majors/index.html">Explore our programs</a>
        </div>
    </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <ul class="rvt-card-grid [ rvt-m-top-xl ] ">
                            <li>
            <div class="rvt-card rvt-card--feature rvt-card--clickable">
                                                                    <div class="rvt-card__image">
                        <img alt="Nursing student checks a patient’s vital signs while a faculty member observes in a hospital room." src="/images/research/index/nursing.webp"/>
                    </div>
                                <div class="rvt-card__body">
                                        <h2 class="rvt-card__title">
                                                    <a href="/academics/degrees-majors/interests/index.html">Programs that shape the field</a>
                                            </h2>
                                            <div class="rvt-card__content">
                            <p>Home to nationally recognized programs across disciplines, faculty prepare graduates to contribute from day one—bringing knowledge and perspective into the world where it matters.</p>
                        </div>
                                    </div>
            </div>
        </li>
                            <li>
            <div class="rvt-card rvt-card--feature rvt-card--clickable">
                                                                    <div class="rvt-card__image">
                        <img alt="Student paints a canvas on an easel while studying fine arts in a campus studio." src="/images/index/painter.webp"/>
                    </div>
                                <div class="rvt-card__body">
                                        <h2 class="rvt-card__title">
                                                    <a href="/academics/index.html">Build perspective across disciplines</a>
                                            </h2>
                                            <div class="rvt-card__content">
                            <p>Grounded in a liberal arts foundation, IU Bloomington fosters critical thinking, curiosity, and the ability to approach complex problems from multiple perspectives—skills that drive impact across every field.</p>
                        </div>
                                    </div>
            </div>
        </li>
                            <li>
            <div class="rvt-card rvt-card--feature rvt-card--clickable">
                                                                    <div class="rvt-card__image">
                        <img alt="Students adjust and test a robotic device during advanced engineering research." src="/images/index/liberal-arts-foundation1.webp"/>
                    </div>
                                <div class="rvt-card__body">
                                        <h2 class="rvt-card__title">
                                                    <a href="/academics/experiential-learning/research-opportunities/index.html">Research happening now—join in</a>
                                            </h2>
                                            <div class="rvt-card__content">
                            <p>From advancing medical treatments to developing new technologies, IU research is shaping real outcomes. Students contribute alongside faculty, building skills while helping move that work forward.</p>
                        </div>
                                    </div>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>                                            </div>
        </div>
                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rvt-section rvt-theme-crimson " data-sb-section="callout">
