        </div>
        <div class="rvt-billboard__body">
                    <p class="rvt-billboard__eyebrow">Research</p>
                            <h2 class="rvt-billboard__title">A research university at full power</h2>
                            <div class="rvt-billboard__content">
                                    <p>Indiana University research moves beyond theory into action&#8212;improving patient care, advancing technology, and informing policy across Indiana and beyond. Trusted to tackle complex challenges across fields, our work creates breakthroughs that improve lives while strengthening industries and driving economic growth throughout the state.</p>
